</reference></task><task class="- topic/topic task/task " id="unique_7" topicrefclass="- map/topicref " nd:nd-id="Analyze_data" oid="Analyze_data" specializations="@props/deliveryTarget">
    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">Analyzing data from paranormal investigation</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">Data that has recorded paranormal phenomenon often need to be adjusted before
        presenting. </shortdesc>
    <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
        <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Data collected from a paranormal investigation can be explored in multiple ways but
                often follow a common procedure</p>
        </context>
        <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Backup data in multiple places</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Download image and audio editors</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Slow down, speed up, and/or change the tonal settings on audio to hear voices</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Alter the lighting and color in images and video</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Save alterations to a common source like USB or external hard drive</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Present evidence for collaborative analysis with others</cmd>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
</task></concept><concept break-before="true" is-chapter="true" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " id="unique_8" topicrefclass="- map/topicref " nd:nd-id="paranormal_investigation" oid="paranormal_investigation" specializations="@props/deliveryTarget">
    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">Paranormal investigation</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">Paranormal investigation is the investigation of unseen or yet unproven phenomena. </shortdesc>
    <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
        <p class="- topic/p ">Paranormal investigation is the practice of gathering information about unseen entities.
            Entities can include ghosts, cryptids, aliens, or other entities. Investigations take
            place in many settings including homes and businesses. </p>
        <p class="- topic/p ">Investigators may be contacted directly by a property manager or person who has seen or
            experienced something paranormal. In many cases, investigators offer their services free
            of charge in exchange for the rights to the evidence they collect during the
            investigation. </p>
    </conbody>
</concept></map>